Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有相聚 就会有分离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这永远的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经历过许多的相聚和分离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈都去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没有地方可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为这个相遇就像是泡沫那么瞬间短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}永远的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道次由我来拍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我帮你擦嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都几岁人了还那么亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天工作结束的真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会在后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为吸血鬼这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要讲没有是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候也想在太阳公公下面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受下日光浴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到海边去游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起自己还是人类的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么还想再做一次的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不太记得 像你一样自己还是人类时的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我并不是那种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和紫藤先生到底是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你新生命 应该算是亲子关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是遭受同样命运的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是属于同伴关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这些并不是你想要的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就不想要得到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以后还能像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无事的生活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事件发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:04:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的 那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点清醒过来 理保
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母已经死了 被夜灵给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父母腐朽的肉体被夜灵附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清醒一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想他们变成那种样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么会是你父母的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只是想利用那样子来迷惑你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理…保…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇定一点 你应该能够了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种情况下没有别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别不出声 你也讲讲话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道没有其他的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈都还记得我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都还拥有人性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我有必要让你了解他们已经死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打败坏人的正义使者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的心很软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有人去保护的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想讲自己是特别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是…吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…你想讲和人类不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼比人类还要厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食物的方面怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有弥生这种血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是活不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲得对 我也不想饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在更不想留在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗？不追过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不可能会有永远的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有相遇就一定会有分离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我早就了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从第一次看到她的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你想等她自己回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 看来你很担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在吸血鬼的功力还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有人看着她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有理保的事务所变得很冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了闻香的咖啡 也在厨房里沾满灰尘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人照顾的仙人掌也枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道被害者的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上没有什么特别严重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的外伤就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血液大多被吸干了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是理保…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情还不能那么快下定论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是事件和她关系最大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们有目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人看见被害人和一个像高中生的女孩讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把她给…杀掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱讲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果真的是理保做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是个死刑实施者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会认为自己是特别的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤是打败坏人的正义使者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是理保做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没资格杀死她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是找不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她已经离开这个城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她想怎么去做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不在我视线范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了事件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那时候他没和我打招呼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情还有救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样讲 对我们有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果早知道会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时就和爸爸妈妈一起死去最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保 不要再闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果第一次错 我还能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别再去侵犯人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我会对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀我吗？杀掉我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个是你的女儿也是同伴的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会罢休的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会继续在这夜里吸人血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到真的是理保
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子决定了就不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在介意什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就像是家畜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你想吃多少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么认为自己是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是吸血鬼 被选中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只是不死不老而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样就觉得高人一等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想想自己本来也是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我一样 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了活下去一定要吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须永远的吸取人血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想能够二个人一起永远生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够这样继续下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然想起界所讲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于作为吸血鬼的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是站在人类之上的王而深信不疑的界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那样无法原谅他那种想法的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时就重复着那家伙同样的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还有一点是完全不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少理保她相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有理保在身边 你就会觉得很放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把自己认为和界一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲得对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳要下山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚又要来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝望之幕又将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不赶快回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被坏人给抓走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再做傻事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想怎么做 是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左边还是右边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士优先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我没诉过你 我不相信女权主义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想伤害她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是理保 不是夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点清醒吧 理保
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来讲 死去的父母和现在的紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪边比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是发过誓要和紫藤一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的同甘共苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生根本不接受我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在一起 我的心也是孤单一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的永远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保是你自愿选择与紫藤在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是何时开始为点小事而斤斤计较
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样紫藤太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:18:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错吧 是紫藤先生教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道自己在做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕哩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个理保应该不可能办得到这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰哩啰嗦的 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保…你到底到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 你不是理保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的你的灵魂并不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧 理保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本不想要得到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是食物中毒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕哩 你想被干掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我给你点新鲜的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬得特别深的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这笨蛋 吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真失礼 你讲谁是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把放在你心底的感情给重新叫醒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼是永生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的幻象也是你的杰作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讲过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那全都是你锁在心底的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在应该了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去你那时候的我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来把你还给紫藤是做对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连吸血鬼都做不好的紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是因为你才能够变得独当一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准你对理保动歪脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是讲过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么呢？我和你的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有相遇就会有分离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会像是河面上的泡沫那样痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:23:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要现在…过得幸运就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 谁把门给锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波に漂う　月の光　昏睡の中　月の光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走る　独り　暗い　空を　あなたに逢えるなら
